snippet.textDisplay:
The only shepherd’s pie that I’ve ever eaten that lived up to my fantasy of what shepherd’s pie might taste like was at Fanelli’s, in Soho, and this one looks like it might actually be better.

That said, while I’m all for having my proverbial pants blown off, if your demi glace is causing people to blow their literal pants off, I think that you might want to reconsider the recipe.
